channel.title: Comments on: Urban Decay Revolution Lipstick Spectacular

item.title: By: Suzi
item.dc:creator: Suzi
item.description: They all look seriously great on you! I'm consistently amazed by how good most of these shades can look on different skin tones. I'm as pale as a ghost, but Jilted, Catfight, F Bomb, and Naked are all really flattering. I'm guessing Native and Protest might not work as well. Or at least that's what I'll keep telling myself so I'm not bummed over missing this deal!
